This package uses Template Haskell to automatically derive instances
of the JSON class from the json package on hackage.

This is a prerelease version but may be distributed under the terms of
the BSD3 license.

Similar projects:
* Rjson: Uses syb-with-class and its own JSON library.
* pugs-drift: Uses DrIFT and its own JSON library (serialization only,
  no deserialization).
